title: 12/24/21  DPS Hour 1  Doug Gottlieb & Jason McIntyre Guest Hosting -  Jimmy G comes up short
itunes:title: 12/24/21  DPS Hour 1  Doug Gottlieb & Jason McIntyre Guest Hosting -  Jimmy G comes up short
description:
Doug and Jason break down the Thursday Night game between the 49ers and Titans, and how Jimmy Garoppolo just didn't deliver in the loss against a Tennessee team that did what they needed to do to win. The guys talk about the Bills-Patriots game this weekend and what the Bills need to do to avenge their loss a few weeks ago in Buffalo. Doug and Jason discuss the end of the name "Staples Center" and how overblown the media reaction has been to that, and give their thoughts on how mediocre the Lakers are at this point of the season.
